---
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
import { SHOP_URL } from "../consts";
---

<Layout
	title="About these reviews"
	description="How Memorygram collects and publishes customer reviews."
	pubDate={new Date("2026-05-24")}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<p>
		This is the home for customer reviews of <a href={SHOP_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener"
			>Memorygram</a
		> — personalized keepsakes and memory gifts, from engraved photo plaques and audio message
		keepsakes to custom star maps and memorial wind chimes.
	</p>

	<p>
		Every review here comes from a real customer. Reviews are collected after purchase and from
		trusted platforms, then published as-is. We show the good and the bad: ratings range across
		the full one-to-five-star scale, and we don't hide critical feedback.
	</p>

	<p>
		Want to share your own experience? Reach out at <a href="mailto:info@memorygram.com"
			>info@memorygram.com</a
		> and we'll add your review.
	</p>
</Layout>
